.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
PakIt provides:
.INDENT 0.0
.IP 1. 3
A Package Manager CLI to install, remove & update programs.
.IP 2. 3
A simple Recipe specification to build programs from source code.
.IP 3. 3
Premade recipes for common programs under \fBpakit_recipes\fP\&.
.UNINDENT
